summary: My newest follower based off of a character from my fanfiction - Skyrim's Finest! Thief, Archer, vampire extraordinaire!
descriptionHtml:
My newest follower based off of a character from my fanfiction - Skyrim's Finest! I present to you.....
Nathaniel the thief of the group. :P he can be found outside Riften's front gate.

Info about Nathaniel:
Nathaniel: Thief, Archer, vampire extraordinaire! He is good with sneak, archery, and has drain life spell. he also has some skill in one handed weapons.


Bugs:

May or may not work with UFO

Requirements:

Skyrim (like always)

use nmm (please please please do!)
